NEW!

A full FM save in one video, in supercut/movie style, follow my journey from taking over as manager of UD Melilla in the Spanish lower leagues. Melilla is a Spanish city, but is geographically located on the continent of Africa - bordered by Morocco. In this challenge, I decide to see if I can take Melilla to the very top of European football - but by only signing African players. There are heroes, villains, trials and tribulations... I hope you enjoy.
